quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,64,"Kaa ko hommbo woni pu…ó…óu…óo tagoore nde refti O rutta ngu, e ko hommbo arsikata on immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Enee, ko dewetee…óo goo wond'ude e Alla? Maaku: "Addee daliili moo…óon on si tawii ko on gooŇč…óu…ďe"."
  27,65,"Maaku: "Anndaa ko wirnii kon …ďen won…ďe ka kammuuli e ka leydi si wonaa Alla. ∆Āe so'ataa kadi ko honnde tuma …ďe immintinoytee"."
  27,66,"Ko woni, ganndal ma…ď…ďe ngal hattii fii Laakara on, ko woni, kam…ďe he…ďe e sikke fii [Laakara], ko woni, kam…ďe ko …ďe wumu…ďe fii …óum."
  27,67,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe mbi'i: " Enee, hay si min laatike mbullaari e baabiraa…ďe amen …ďen kadi, e hara minen ko min yaltinoytee…ďe?""
  27,68,"GooŇč…óii min podanooma …óum minen e baabiraa…ďe amen ko adii, …óum wonaani si wonaa tinndi adinoo…ďe."
  27,69,"Maaku : "njehee ka leydi ndaaron ko honno battane bon…ďe …ďen laatornoo"."
  27,70,"Wota a suno fii ma…ď…ďe, wota a laato e …ďitteende immorde e ko …ďe peewjata kon."
  27,71,"He…ďe mb'a: "Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike gooŇču…ó…ďe?""
  27,72,"Maaku: "No tijjaa de tawata …ďadanike on yoga e kon ko …óa…ď…ďu…óon yaccinaneede"."
  27,73,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa ko O Jom ∆Āural e dow yim…ďe …ďeen, kono …ďur…ďe …óuu…óude …ďen e ma…ď…ďe …ďe njaarnataa [Alla]."
  27,74,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa hiMo Anndi ko …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen coomi e ko …óe 'e√Ī√Īinta ko."
  27,75,"Alaa e birniikum ka kammu e ka leydi si wonaa [fii makkun] no e ndeer deftere …ďanngunde."
  27,76,"Pellet ndee Alqur'aanaare, hende filloo e dow …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen fii hu'unde nde …ďe …ďuri luutondirde nden e fii muu…óum."